    "headline": "Carrier Board of Directors Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend",
    "summary": "Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE:CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, announced today that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly dividend of $0.24 per outstanding share of Carrier common stock. The dividend will be payable on May 22, 2026 to shareowners of record at the close of business on May 4, 2026.",
